# Open Slap — Environment Variables (example)

# Router (MoE) — LLM-first expert selection
# When OPENSLAP_ROUTER_PROVIDER is NOT set (or is off/false/0), the router falls back to keyword routing with no extra timeout.
# Set to enable LLM-first selection (adds one small LLM call per message to pick the best expert).

# OPENSLAP_ROUTER_PROVIDER=groq
# OPENSLAP_ROUTER_MODEL=llama-3.1-8b-instant
# OPENSLAP_ROUTER_TIMEOUT_S=2.0

